entcube/code_interpreter.py:200\n- ✅ `list_files(path)` - agentcube/code_interpreter.py:215\n\n**Instance fields**: All specified fields present\n- ✅ `name`, `namespace`, `ttl`, `verbose`, `logger`, `cp_client`, `router_url`, `session_id`, `dp_client`\n\n---\n\n### ✅ **`AgentRuntimeClient` - COMPLIANT**\n\n**Constructor**: All parameters match spec exactly\n- ✅ `agent_name: str`\n- ✅ `namespace: str = \"default\"`\n- ✅ `router_url: Optional[str] = None`\n- ✅ `verbose: bool = False`\n- ✅ `session_id: Optional[str] = None`\n- ✅ `timeout: int = 120`\n- ✅ `connect_timeout: float = 5.0`\n\n**Methods**: All methods present and signatures match spec\n- ✅ `__enter__()` - agentcube/agent_runtime.py:61\n- ✅ `__exit__()` - agentcube/agent_runtime.py:69\n- ✅ `invoke(payload, timeout)` - agentcube/agent_runtime.py:79\n- ✅ `close()` - agentcube/agent_runtime.py:98\n\n**Instance fields**: All specified fields present\n- ✅ `agent_name`, `namespace`, `timeout`, `connect_timeout`, `logger`, `router_url`, `session_id`, `dp_client`\n\n---\n\n### ✅ **`ControlPlaneClient` - COMPLIANT**\n\n**Constructor**: All parameters match spec exactly\n- ✅ `workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None`\n- ✅ `auth_token: Optional[str] = None`\n- ✅ `timeout: int = 120`\n- ✅ `connect_timeout: float = 5.0`\n- ✅ `pool_connections: int = 10`\n- ✅ `pool_maxsize: int = 10`\n\n**Methods**: All methods present and signatures match spec\n- ✅ `create_session(name, namespace, metadata, ttl)` - agentcube/clients/control_plane.py:50\n- ✅ `delete_session(session_id)` - agentcube/clients/control_plane.py:99\n- ✅ `close()` - agentcube/clients/control_plane.py:133\n\n**HTTP endpoints**: Match spec exactly\n- ✅ `POST {base_url}/v1/code-interpreter` - agentcube/clients/control_plane.py:75\n- ✅ `DELETE {base_url}/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/{session_id}` - agentcube/clients/control_plane.py:112\n- ✅ Headers: `Content-Type`, `Authorization` (when token present)\n- ✅ Timeout: `(connect_timeout, timeout)` on each request\n\n-